rows.label: qst201406_msg0001
rows.name:
Hello Hikari. Hello Zakuro.
What are Hikari and Zakuro doing?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0002
rows.name:
Hana! You turned up at
just the right time!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0003
rows.name:
As it happens, Zakuro and I are facing off
to see who has the most Girl Power.
We'd like to ask you to judge.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0004
rows.name: Understood! Hana here to help!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0005
rows.name:
Hana's just the sort to give us an
impartial measurement of our Girl
Power!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0006
rows.name:
Okay! We can talk about some real
girl stuff now. Who we're into!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0007
rows.name: That's what it's all about, huh?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0008
rows.name:
Zakuro... Can't you change it up a bit?
You're obsessed with this topic...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0009
rows.name: How about you, Hana?

rows.label: qst201406_msg0010
rows.name:
Hey, I'd be pretty curious to hear how
you'd answer that, Hana!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0011
rows.name:
Hana not really sure what Zakuro is
talking about.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0012
rows.name:
We're telling each other who our
special someone is, Hana.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0013
rows.name: I mean, like, who do you like...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0014
rows.name: Hana likes everyone!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0015
rows.name: Ah, no... That's not what she means.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0016
rows.name:
Hana think Girl Power have other
aspects. Like organizing life and
fulfilling goals.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0017
rows.name:
Hana have extensive sub-routines and
software libraries for making life
successful.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0018
rows.name:
Based on criteria like task-completion,
punctuality and efficiency, Hana have
much Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0019
rows.name: Erm...I guess she's right...

rows.label: qst201406_msg0020
rows.name:
Ah...yeah, I have a bit of a blind spot
for that sort of thing.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0021
rows.name:
So according to Hana's calculations,
winner is Hana! Please applaud!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0022
rows.name: Hey...we can't settle it just like that!

rows.label: qst201406_msg0023
rows.name:
Yeah... We've got no hope of winning
against Hana's robotic brain.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0024
rows.name: Looks like another draw.

rows.label: qst201406_msg0025
rows.name: Yup.
